===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[calculate]]; to [[estimate]]; to [[reckon]]
#* {{zh-x|我 商 賚{lài} 爾。|I will '''calculate''' [your merits] and bestow rewards upon you.|ref=Shangshu}}
#* {{zh-x|能 商 功利。|able to '''calculate''' achievements and benefits|ref=Hanshu}}
# to [[discuss]]; to [[consult]]; to [[deliberate]]
#* {{zh-x|成敗 之 來，先史 商 之 久 矣。|The coming of success and failure has been '''deliberated''' upon by earlier historians for a long time.|ref=Houhanshu}}
# {{lb|zh|of merchants}} to [[trade]]; to do [[business]]; [[commerce]]
#* {{zh-x|或 漁 或 商|some fishing, some '''trading'''|ref={{lw|zh|郭璞}}《江賦》}}
# [[businessman]]; [[dealer]]; [[trader]]; [[merchant]]
#: {{zh-also|商賈}}
#* {{zh-x|富家 之 商，必 奪 貧室 之 財。|'''Merchants''' of wealthy houses will certainly snatch away the property of poor families.|ref=Lunheng-F}}
# {{lb|zh|music}} the second [[note]] in the Chinese [[pentatonic scale]], equivalent to "2" in numbered musical notation
#* {{zh-x|引 商 刻 羽，雜 以 流 徵{zhǐ}。|Drawing out '''shāng''' and incising yǔ, intermingled with flowing zhǐ.|ref=Wenxuan}}
# {{lb|zh|literary}} [[autumn]] {{gl|the ''shāng'' note was associated with autumn in ancient Chinese five-phase cosmology}}
#* {{zh-x|商 風 肅 而 害 生 兮|The '''autumn''' wind blows harshly and harms living things|ref=Chuci}}
#* {{zh-x|今 兹 商 用事，餘 熱 亦 已 末。|Now '''autumn''' holds sway, and the lingering heat has come to an end.|ref=8th century, {{lw|zh|杜甫}}, {{lang|zh|《七月三日……戲呈元二十一曹長》}}}}
# {{lb|zh|astronomy}} {{zh-altname|心|{{w|Heart (Chinese constellation)|Heart}} mansion, one of the {{w|Twenty-Eight Mansions}}; also called {{zh-l|商星}}}}
#* {{zh-x|人生 不 相見，動 如 參{Shēn} 與 商。|In life we do not meet, like the stars Shēn and '''Shāng''' [that never appear together in the sky].|ref=8th century, {{lw|zh|杜甫}}, {{lang|zh|《贈衛八處士》}}}}
# {{lb|zh|historical}} a [[division]] on the indicator rod of an ancient [[water clock]]; a unit roughly equal to a quarter hour
#* {{zh-x|日 入 三 商 為 昏。|Three '''shāng''' after sunset is dusk.|ref={{w|Zheng Xuan}}, commentary on {{lang|zh|《儀禮·士昏禮》}}}}
# {{zh-div|朝}} the {{w|Shang dynasty}} (c. 1600 – 1046 {{BCE}})
# {{lb|zh|historical}} {{n-g|alternative name for the state of {{w|Song (state)|Song}} during the {{w|Spring and Autumn period}}, as the ruling house descended from the Shang royal family}}
#* {{zh-x|闕 為 深溝，通 於 商 魯 之 間。|[They] breached [the dikes] to form deep channels, connecting through to the region between '''Song''' and Lu.|ref=Guoyu}}
# {{lb|zh|historical}} {{n-g|name of various ancient places:}}
## the fief of {{w|Xie (Shang dynasty)|Xie}}, progenitor of the Shang dynasty, in present-day {{w|Shangluo}}, [[Shaanxi]]
## a Warring States period location in present-day {{w|Xichuan County}}, [[Henan]], where {{w|Shang Yang}} was enfeoffed
